-title "Team"
%h1.margin-top Padrino Team
.content
  Padrino exists because of these members. each of them has committed their time and effort in the creation 
  and improvement of this project. The team consists of programmers all over, such as Italy and the US.
  Because of their hard work, Padrino has come into existence!
  
%ul.team
  -Account.all.each do |account|
    %li
      .avatar
        - link_to account.home_page do
          =image_tag(account.gravatar(100), :alt => account.name)
      .description
        %h3=account.full_name
        =account.description_html
      .clear